    			<div  class="right_content" >
    				<h3 style="text-align:center;color:rgb(67,67,67);font-size:20px;">寻找中国合伙人，每年有上千亿的消费市场，持续发展无忧！</h3>
				<div style="color:rgb(67,67,67);" class="content_detail"><p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 25.59375px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">泉州市洁立康环保工程有限公司是一家专业研发生产销售环保设备、智能自来水管清洗机、多功能家电清洗设备、空气净化设备、清洁用品、清洁工具、水系统净化服务的创新环保企业。公司拥有先进的生产技术，更有一批具有创新精神的专业技术人才和服务团队。</span></p><p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 25.59375px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p><p><img src="/jlk/lib/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170113/1484268040703139.jpg"/></p><p><img src="/jlk/lib/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170113/1484269576120209.jpg" title="1484269576120209.jpg" alt="416358507769619088.jpg"/></p><p><img src="/jlk/lib/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170113/1484269589139031.jpg" title="1484269589139031.jpg" alt="588567432946052706.jpg"/></p><p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 25.59375px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 宋体; line-height: 25.59375px; text-indent: 27px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">洁立康的智能自来水管道清洗机，是以气和水为介质，通过专用水管清洗机产生顺洗、逆洗、涡流、水槌、震荡剥离等周波，逐层剥落锈垢和存积物并快速排除管外，达到清洗目的，对管道无腐蚀，排放无污染而且有效地净化水质。</span></span><br/></p><p><img src="/jlk/lib/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170113/1484269767106955.jpg" title="1484269767106955.jpg" alt="1-1F10400312I94.jpg"/></p><p><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 1.6; text-indent: 28px; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">水是生命之源，居家过日子，自来水管道与人们的生活和生命息息相关。但是很多人</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 1.6; text-indent: 28px; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">不知道，使用年久的供水管道，由于水在管内的流动，氧化反应会生成铁锈，在管道安装、</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 1.6; text-indent: 28px; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">破损维修时进入管内的泥沙在管内沉积，致使管内径变小，水流量不足，供水不畅，严重</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 1.6; text-indent: 28px; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">时造成管道堵塞无法供水。</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 1.6; text-indent: 28px; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">此外，由于水源水质下降和二次供水污染，水中的各种微生物繁衍，导致水中的细菌和病毒有害物质增多，</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; text-indent: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 1.6; text-indent: 28px; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">对人的身体健康构成</span><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 1.6; text-indent: 28px; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">严重的威胁。</span></p><p><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 1.6; text-indent: 28px; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/jlk/lib/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170113/1484269837693198.jpg" title="1484269837693198.jpg" alt="1-1F10400321C25.jpg"/></span></p><p><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 1.6; text-indent: 28px; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(101, 100, 100); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-indent: 28px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">清洗原理：</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(101, 100, 100); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 21px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-indent: 28px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;">1<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">、高周波震荡剥离：水管内真空产生高周波，制造大量水泡，水泡破裂震荡使异物剥离管壁。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(101, 100, 100); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 21px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-indent: 28px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;">2<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">、螺旋侧面环洗：水流以螺旋波方式冲洗管壁凹陷细缝卡垢。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(101, 100, 100); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 21px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-indent: 28px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;">3<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">、水槌直冲：压力震波产生强劲水槌，直接冲洗水管内污垢</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(101, 100, 100); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 21px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-indent: 28px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;">4<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">、快速回来逆洗：水波以顺逆双向快速来回，反复冲洗管壁。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(101, 100, 100); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-indent: 28px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">问题解答：</span></strong></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(101, 100, 100); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 21px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-indent: 28px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;">1<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">、好像没听过洗水管，只有洗水塔？</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(101, 100, 100); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 21px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-indent: 28px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">答：日本早在二十几年前就开始清洗水管，台湾也是早几年就已经有清洗水管新技术，在国内清洗水管的服务愈来愈普遍，大家越来越重视健康。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(101, 100, 100); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 21px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-indent: 28px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;">&nbsp;<span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; word-wrap: break-word !important;">2</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.6; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">、家里有装净水器，也需要洗水管？</span></span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(101, 100, 100); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 21px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-indent: 28px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">答：需要！净水器一般放置在厨房，而清洗水管的目的是让家里每个龙头流出的水都尽可能减少污染。使刷牙洗脸、洗手洗澡、洗衣等直接接触的自来水更干净，最重要的是能延长净水器耗材的寿命。</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(101, 100, 100); font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 25.6px; text-indent: 21px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box !important; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; text-indent: 28px; font-family: 宋体; word-wrap: break-word !important;">3<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">、只洗家里的水管有用吗？外面的主供水管就不脏吗？</span></span></p><p><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 1.6; text-indent: 28px; font-family: 宋体; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img src="/jlk/lib/ueditor/php/upload/image/20170113/1484269704800778.jpg" alt="1484269704800778.jpg"/></span><br/></p><p><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin: 